column8:
to listening应改为to listen;
冠词the误用；
I have a little time

1.固定搭配出错，listen to sth.;
2.修饰不定代词的形容词放后面即可，不需要加be动词，直接表达为something normal;
3.主谓不一致，应为everyone speaks it...;
4.结尾处right应改为correctly.
some abnormal expressions

1. want go to 为固定短语使用错误，应改为 want to go to;
2.  i don't go to时态错误，应使用一般过去时
3. 推测irs为IELTS，存在发音问题

首句缺少谓语动词，原因状语从句后半句缺少主语it,宾语air；
when i am confused with something;
dip使用错误，可以改为am

just like后加动词ing形式，make改为making;
比较级错误，删去more;
单复数错误，sentences，加s

yesterday was great 缺少主语，应改为yesterday it was great;
skill需加s， 
do 使用错误, 可改为talk about，can we talk about how to learn English or how to study?

1.时态错误，go应改为went; 
2. 短语使用错误，应是went camping; 
3.camping发音不准
4. Bennetts发音不准确

时态错误，过去式 the goal was like;
won发成want
kind of 后接形容词，可以改为It was kind of boring

复数表达不一致,fur, 删去s;
her改为its;
it's fur is almost

want to show,去掉s;
agriculture是农业改成culture;
组织下语言应该改为I want to show Chinese cultural to the world and let the kids know the rich culture we have.

主谓不一致，it hasn't;
The four thousand yuan hasn't arrived in my bank;
bank是银行 bank account才是账户

改为I don't have coffee machine at home;
difficult发音不准
making a cappuccino for me

用户要求模型回答完后翻译；
invite a loved date改为inviting someone on a love date;
during the conversation you must translate to chat with me possible as possibly改为you should translate every sentence you said during the conversation if possible

第一句feelings应该用单数feeling；
go back前加to;
It seems to be different后面的anymore删去

at that time;
it's him deserve it，他应得的可以表达为he deserves it
(这里用户说吵架可能是说对方不值得，
可改为 every bad word i said to him is that he didn't deserve it)；
hurt使用不当，应该用形容词hurtful;
the words are;
change for me改为change myself;
i will watch...

时态错误，应该用一般过去时did和played;
语序有误改为 I often played this game with my friend;
also不恰当改为often

start应该用过去式started;
用户吞吐;
用lower than比below更合适

I usually(一般现在时) listening to;
it can(情态动词跟原型）makes me;
more energetic and happyness;
bad music可以表达为sad music

the before last question;
you asked me;
how many books

用户表达比较卡壳；
improve my English words改为English vocabulary;
preparing for the;
articles or news reports;
so this is/that is my answer

the time of my answer needs to be controlled in 30 seconds;
可以改为how can I extend my answer in a variety of aspects;
how can I get it do that
